Vcs-Git: git://github.com/xobs/novena-disable-ssp.git
Vcs-Browser: http://github.com/xobs/novena-disable-ssp

Package: novena-disable-ssp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Novena Bluetooth SSP disabler
 SSP is buggy on a lot of USB Bluetooth devices, and can make pairing a
 Bluetooth keyboard very tedious.  This program simply exists to disable
 SSP on any Bluetooth adapter it detects.
